low?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Chris carefully considers each of his meals due to his autoimmune disease diagnosis. He eats a wide variety of nutrient-dense foods such as Atlantic cod and Lean Ground Turkey. His supplements include whey protein isolate and collagen powder.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.endomondo.com/news/chris-bumstead#faq-question-1728998478312","position":4,"url":"https://www.endomondo.com/news/chris-bumstead#faq-question-1728998478312","name":"How did Chris Bumstead influence the bodybuilding world?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Since his Olympia debut, Chris has become a role model to the bodybuilding world and the wider community. He set the standard for classic physique and paved the way for other athletes to follow in his footsteps.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.endomondo.com/news/chris-bumstead#faq-question-1728998486644","position":5,"url":"https://www.endomondo.com/news/chris-bumstead#faq-question-1728998486644","name":"Will Chris Bumstead ever return to competitive bodybuilding?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"While we can't rule this out for certain, it’s highly unlikely that he will return. He now has a family and multiple business ventures to focus on. However, if he ever gets the itch again, he’s young enough.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"},{"@type":"Question","@id":"https://www.endomondo.com/news/chris-bumstead#faq-question-1728998497806","position":6,"url":"https://www.endomondo.com/news/chris-bumstead#faq-question-1728998497806","name":"What legacy does Chris Bumstead leave behind in bodybuilding?","answerCount":1,"acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Chris Bumstead leaves behind a legacy as one of the most iconic and popular figures in the sport. With six titles to his name, he has helped shape and popularize the classic physique division.","inLanguage":"en-US"},"inLanguage":"en-US"}]}</script>
